values:
so in my head i think well lets see 20 yrs old and moved by myself down to south beach for the summer...pretty ballsy i think--ballsy?  ne ways still have two more years of school left but seriously considering moving down here. who knows have prly a total of 20 dollars in my bank account left and i have one and half months left.  yeah the parents are helping me big time- but im still pretty stressed about it.  also im gonna go to some modeling agencies ---my dream right there. and really this summer will really i believe define the next couple years of my life which makes me pretty nervous.  i feel as though im split right down the middle.  miami one side and my life in michigan the other side.  its just so different here than it is there.  i like this life, but i would like it more if i had a steady job and income...not just an internship but im sure this internship would help me out--- i don't fucking know...

just thinking out loud.

<font color="#333300" size="4">so i leave for ireland in a couple of days, and im so excited! i will be gone for two weeks, and i guess we are sleeping some place different every night which kind of sucks but not a big deal ne ways im excited!</font>

soo i got the job! im pretty excited! i leave for ireland here in a couple of weeks so im also pretty pumped about that! then after ireland i go upnorth for the fourth of july so that exciting! but yeah hope everyone had a good weekend!

<font color="#339966" size="4">so today is my real first job interview, and im 18 lol what does that tell you. anyways i applied to "the buckle" one of my fav stores so kind of excited! well wish me luck!</font>

<font color="#993366" size="4">Well hello everyone.  So this is brand new...I thought i have everything else so why not live journal lol! ne ways i'm writing a quick hello to everyone before im off to bed.  Kind of excited about this, not going to lie loL!</font>
